# Changelog

## [1.1.3] - 2026-03-15
### Fixed
- Recorder tower placement after Hologram ability
    - Recorder now no longer places a tower after Hologram ability is used

## [1.1.2] - 2026-03-13
### Fixed
- Tower stacking logging
    - The recorder now automatically detects Stack Tower UI state to apply true flag in recorder strats

## [1.1.1] - 2026-03-11
### Fixed
- Recorder spamming duplicate ability logs
    - The recorder will no longer log abilities that are already handled by Auto-UI toggles (DJ Booth, Commander, Necromancer)

## [1.1.0] - 2026-03-07
### Added
- Initial project files
- Medic logic and elevate Recorder hook thread identity
    - The recorder will now correctly log every ability (Medic, Mercenary base, DJ etc.)
- Trial elevator teleport
    - The library now actually teleports to the Trial elevator when calling TDS:Mode("Trial") function
- Trial and Special detection
    - The recorder skips TDS:GameInfo() if Special or Trial mode is detected

### Fixed
- UnlockSpeedTickets crash when the TimeScale UI option is pre-enabled
	- TDS:UnlockTimeScale() will no longer cause an error if Timescale is pre-enabled in the UI

### Changed
- Updated loadstrings to local repo
- Removed npc:Destroy() logic in AntiLag to prevent lag issues
